text:
{
  "prompt": "An electric utility bike inspired by the UBCO Utility Bike, customized for food delivery. It features a step-through chrome silver frame with no top tube, a front 26-inch road tire with suspension fork, and a rear 20-inch CST Big Boat tire with a rear air suspension. The bike is equipped with a Bafang mid-drive motor and an internal gear hub. The battery is integrated into the lower downtube box structure. The design includes front and rear racks for cargo. Overall look is clean, sturdy, and modern, with a hint of pop art-inspired paint patterns on a white base.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution side profile image of a modern electric utility bike inspired by the UBCO style. The bike has a polished silver step-through frame with an integrated black battery in the downtube. It features a 26-inch front wheel and a noticeably smaller 20-inch rear wheel for a distinct size contrast. The rear includes a visible air shock absorber (rear suspension), a cargo rack, and disc brakes. The front fork is suspension-equipped. The bike sits on a flat gray studio background with clean lighting, emphasizing the size difference between the wheels.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution side view of a modern electric utility bike with a chrome step-through frame. The bike features a visibly smaller 20-inch rear wheel and a larger 26-inch front wheel with a suspension fork. It includes a central motor with a mid-drive system, a rear cargo rack, and most importantly, a rear air suspension shock absorber clearly visible above the rear wheel. The frame is clean and minimal, with an integrated battery along the downtube. The background is a neutral studio gray.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution profile image of a sleek, white electric utility bike with modern styling. The bike has a front 26-inch road tire with standard width and a rear 20-inch road tire with a noticeably wider profile. The bike features a rear suspension, disc brakes, and an integrated battery within a step-through chrome frame. The saddle is mounted on an adjustable seat post, like a regular bicycle, allowing height adjustments. The front and rear tires are clearly different in diameter and width, shown clearly from a true side view on a neutral background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution side profile of a white electric utility bike with a sleek, step-through frame. The design includes a visibly extended rear triangle for enhanced rear suspension geometry, allowing for a smoother articulation of the shock absorber. The bike has a mid-drive motor and a belt or chain transmission connected to the rear wheel. The rear wheel is 20 inches with a wide on-road tire, and the front wheel is 26 inches with a standard road tire. The seat is height adjustable, and the overall structure prioritizes both practicality and mechanical integrity. A black battery pack is integrated in the down tube, and the front and rear suspension are clearly visible. The bike is set against a clean, neutral gray background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution digital concept rendering of an electric motorcycle inspired by the Honda PCX125, but with a unique 'Chunbong' design identity. It features an underbone-style aluminum frame with a visually low center of gravity, centrally mounted mid-drive 5000W motor, and a 72V 125Ah battery seamlessly integrated into the lower frame section. The design emphasizes utility, with a robust and efficient rear cargo rack system, ideal for food delivery or travel. The vehicle retains bicycle-like aesthetics while incorporating scooter-level power, with a sleek and practical modern urban look. The tires are road-oriented, with a larger front wheel and slightly smaller rear. The image is a side profile view with clean lighting and white background, showcasing the structural geometry clearly.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution side-view digital rendering of a futuristic electric delivery bike designed for 14-hour workdays. The bike features a large central battery compartment integrated into an underbone frame, a step-through design with a visible mid-drive motor, and full front and rear racks for cargo. The rear wheel is smaller (20-inch wide on-road tire), the front wheel is larger (26-inch slim on-road tire), creating a visually distinct wheel size difference. The rear suspension is clearly visible, and there is no front suspension fork. The saddle includes a pronounced lumbar support (pelvic support ridge) and is ergonomically shaped for comfort. The footrests are positioned slightly forward, mimicking a semi-reclined scooter-style posture. The overall design emphasizes functionality, rider comfort, and long-distance efficiency, with minimalistic yet industrial styling.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution digital illustration of a modern electric motorcycle inspired by an underbone frame, featuring a comfortable riding posture designed for long delivery shifts. The bike includes a prominent rear suspension, a thick saddle with a pelvic support ridge, and forward-positioned footrests similar to a Harley-Davidson cruiser. A rider is shown seated on the bike, leaning slightly back with legs extended forward, hands on wide handlebars. The overall styling is sleek but practical, with a white-black color scheme and efficient cargo racks. Urban city street background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A futuristic electric utility motorcycle with a rider in a relaxed, Harley-Davidson-style cruising position. The rider is seated on a low, wide saddle with a pronounced lumbar (pelvic) support, and their feet are comfortably stretched forward to footrests near the front wheel, like a cruiser motorcycle. The handlebars are pulled back slightly, allowing the rider to sit upright or slightly reclined with shoulders relaxed. The motorcycle has an underbone frame, a central motor, a low-mounted large battery, and wide tires. The style merges utility and comfort — like a modern electric bike designed for 14-hour delivery work. Background is neutral, full side view.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A futuristic electric touring motorcycle styled like a Honda Goldwing but in a minimalist step-through frame similar to a bicycle. The rider is seated in a relaxed, reclined touring position with legs extended forward onto wide footboards, and the back supported by a high backrest. The rider is wearing simple urban riding gear, not racing leathers. The design emphasizes comfort, long-range riding, and utility. The bike has an underbone frame, a large rear cargo rack, and a sleek integrated battery pack. High-resolution digital rendering, side view.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution digital photograph of a futuristic electric delivery bike with an underbone frame, large battery compartment, and no visible rider. The bike has a comfortable cruiser-style seat, forward footrests, and a wide rear rack mounted with a large insulated delivery bag. The front is clean and aerodynamic, and the overall color is white with black trim. The setting is a neutral studio background.",
  "referenced_image_ids": ["file_000000003a4c62438b7ec0bd38c857aa"]
}

{
  "prompt": "A futuristic electric touring bike inspired by the Honda Gold Wing, with a comfortable step-through frame, a wide cushioned seat with a lumbar support backrest, forward-extended footrests, and high handlebars. The bike is equipped with hard panniers and a large rear delivery box, suitable for long-distance delivery. The frame design emphasizes stability and comfort, and the overall weight appears substantial but well-balanced. The bike has a modern matte-black and silver finish, viewed from a 3/4 front perspective in a neutral studio setting.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A futuristic electric motorcycle with a bicycle-inspired underbone frame design, retaining minimalist styling and practicality like the 'Chunbong' prototype. The vehicle includes a mid-mounted motor, a large 72V battery pack integrated into the frame, a wide ergonomic seat with a lumbar support backrest, and forward-positioned footrests (similar to a cruiser style). The overall shape keeps a lightweight and open-frame bicycle aesthetic (visible tubing, slim frame elements), but equipped with high-end components: dual disc brakes, LED lighting, and a functional rear rack for delivery bags. The riding position mimics Honda Goldwing's comfort, but the frame and silhouette clearly retain a heritage rooted in bicycle design, not a full-size motorcycle.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A 3D-rendered digital image of an electric utility motorcycle with a heritage inspired by a bicycle frame. The design features a straight-line, underbone-style frame with minimal curves. The body has no fuel tank, emphasizing that it's fully electric. It includes a central battery pack integrated into the frame, a low seat with a backrest, forward-mounted footrests, and large rear cargo rack for delivery. The overall shape retains the visual language of a bicycle but has motorcycle-level robustness. Background is neutral studio lighting.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A 3D-rendered digital image of a white electric utility bike with a minimalist, straight-line underbone frame, no gas tank, and clearly visible battery and mid-drive motor placed as low as possible for a low center of gravity. The design preserves a modern bicycle-inspired aesthetic rather than a motorcycle. The frame is geometric and efficient, with flat surfaces and no superfluous parts. The rear has a large cargo rack. There is no visible engine block or exhaust. The overall silhouette is clean and practical, designed for long-range urban delivery use. Background is neutral studio lighting.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A 3D-rendered digital image of an electric utility motorcycle with a clean, minimalist design. The frame is straight and angular, featuring a clear step-through layout with no top tube, making it easy to mount. The motor and battery are mounted low near the bottom bracket area, enhancing stability. The vehicle maintains a bicycle-inspired underbone frame structure. It includes a comfortable seat with lumbar support, front and rear cargo racks, and on-road tires. The overall look is functional but sleek, ideal for urban delivery use.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A 3D-rendered digital image of a white electric utility bike with a step-through frame, comfortable cruiser-style handlebars, and a rear cargo rack with a delivery box mounted. Highlight and label the battery location in the center of the lower frame near the pedals (mid-drive area), showing it as a rectangular unit integrated with the downtube. The frame is simple and straight-lined, with no gas tank. The design retains a bicycle-like look but is clearly electric. Background is clean and neutral.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A realistic technical render of a step-through electric bike inspired by the Eahora Juliet 2 frame, shown in side view. The bike is equipped with a centrally mounted large battery pack located inside the lower main frame triangle, similar to the Eahora Juliet. A mid-drive electric motor is positioned at the bottom bracket area, clearly visible. Below and slightly behind the motor is a compact scooter-style CVT (Continuously Variable Transmission) gearbox connected to the drivetrain. The bike has a clean, modern utilitarian look with fat tires and a rear rack. The frame design is straight and efficient, maintaining an overall bicycle-like silhouette without a gas tank. All components are labeled: 'Battery', 'Mid-drive Motor', and 'CVT Gearbox'.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A 3D-rendered concept image of an electric delivery bike inspired by PCX125-level acceleration. It features a step-through aluminum underbone frame, large battery pack mounted low in the center, a mid-drive 2000W electric motor connected to a CVT transmission, wide rear 20-inch on-road tire (CST Big Boat style), and standard 26-inch front tire (Schwalbe). The frame is straight-lined and modern with a cargo rack in the rear. It has a gel-padded seat with pelvic support and slightly forward footrests for comfortable long-hour riding. The bike includes hydraulic disc brakes, throttle control, and a small digital display. The color scheme is white with black and silver components, presented from a side view.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A realistic digital rendering of a rugged, heavy-duty electric utility bike in a warehouse or industrial alley setting, featuring a strong step-through frame, 26-inch front wheel, 20-inch fat rear tire, and dual suspension. On the bike, a male rider with a stocky build, shaved head, about 183 cm tall and 110 kg, wearing a red shirt and purple shorts, is sitting in a relaxed delivery riding position with feet slightly forward and back straight. He is carrying a delivery bag mounted on the rear rack. The lighting is urban and moody, emphasizing the industrial strength of the bike.",
  "referenced_image_ids": ["file-BPhLmdi3NR4yEsCPYaNzv2"],
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A realistic image of an Asian middle-aged male delivery rider wearing a helmet, sitting confidently on a rugged electric utility bike in a side view, modeled after the uploaded motorcycle image. The rider is wearing a red shirt and purple shorts. The bike has a step-through frame, central motor, and battery pack integrated into the frame. The background is neutral gray.",
  "referenced_image_ids": ["file-CoeYz2EkJNFgFNSuKuxHnz", "file_000000007b5461f5b0e42f1ec23d3d5d"],
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A realistic 3D render of an electric utility bike with a heavy-duty design (step-through frame, mid-drive motor, battery on downtube). Riding the bike is a middle-aged, heavyset Korean man (height 183cm, weight 110kg), wearing a red shirt and purple shorts. He is wearing a bicycle helmet and sitting in a natural pedaling position with both feet on the pedals, back straight, hands on handlebars. The overall feel is that of a strong, urban electric bike rider in control of a powerful delivery bike.",
  "size": "1024x1024",
  "referenced_image_ids": ["file-FRPvEdDivEaMgXf1kYs9Hj"]
}
